DISCLAIMER

NexAura is a hackathon prototype built for educational and demonstration
purposes at the Guidewire DEVTrails 2026 University Hackathon. It is NOT:

  - A licensed insurance product
  - A regulated financial service
  - Approved by IRDAI (Insurance Regulatory and Development Authority of India)
  - Suitable for production use without appropriate regulatory approval

The parametric insurance model, payout amounts, and coverage terms described
in this software are for demonstration only. Any use of this software in a
real financial product requires full compliance with applicable Indian laws
including but not limited to the Insurance Act 1938, IRDAI regulations, and
the Payment and Settlement Systems Act 2007.

The ML models (XGBoost, IsolationForest, Prophet) included in this repository
were trained on synthetic datasets for demonstration. They should not be relied
upon for real financial decisions without retraining on actual production data
and independent validation.

